00:04:25,568 --&gt; 00:03:14,695
try to remove the powder with the knife

00:04:38.736 --> 00:04:47.738
Put the leaf into the tinder bundle

00:04:50.780 --> 00:04:55.657
blow gently from the bottom

00:05:03.699 --> 00:05:05.908
…and you have the fire

